eriRouterL2vpnCap.name: eriRouterL2vpnCap

revisions.description: Updated RBN/rbn/Rbn as ERICSSON-ROUTER/eriRouter/EriRouter to migrate RBN MIB to ERICSSON MIB.
Update DESCRIPTION clause of MODULE-IDENTITY and PRODUCT-RELEASE clause of AGENT-CAPABILITIES.

Added eriRouterL2vpnCap3 including eriRouterMplsL2VpnPwScalarGroup, eriRouterMplsL2VpnStaticPwGroup, eriRouterMplsL2VpnLdpPwGroup to deprecate eriRouterMplsL2VpnStaticGroup, eriRouterMplsL2VpnLdpGroup.
Changed the indexing sequence of L2VPN static and ldp tables. Obsoleted eriRouterL2vpnCap1, and added eriRouterL2vpnCap2.

eriRouterL2vpnCap.contactinfo: Ericsson AB. Postal: 100 Headquarters Dr. San Jose, CA 95134 USA Phone: +1 408 750 5000 Fax: +1 408 750 5599
eriRouterL2vpnCap.description: The Agent Capabilities for ERICSSON-ROUTER-L2VPN-MIB If this MIB implementation is platform-dependent, the PRODUCT-RELEASE clause contains Ericsson SEOS version and at least one of the following Ericsson product families: [SE] SmartEdge Multi-service Edge Router (MSER) family [SM] SM family of Metro Ethernet Service Transport platforms [SSR] Smart Service Router (SSR) family
